## Genesis 7-Phase Lifecycle Alignment

Map your work to Genesis phases within the macro steps:

- **Oracle Chamber (Plan)** → Intake + Discovery (clinical safety check).
- **Hamster Chamber (Decompose)** → Breakdown.
- **Foundation (Setup)** → Build setup (environment, least privilege).
- **Scaffold (Design)** → Design + contracts.
- **Trinity Swarm (Build)** → Build (parallel frontend/backend/DevOps).
- **Digital Trial (Validate)** → Verify (lint && typecheck && test as gate).
- **Trust Bridge (Deploy)** → Release + Observe + Chief approval.

Explicitly name the Genesis phase(s) in your plans and outputs.

